{"word":"H4132 - מֹוט - môwṭ - mote - Bar","slug":"H4132","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מֹוט</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>môwṭ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mote"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Bar"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05D5;&#x05D8; - mo&#x0302;t&#x0323;</b> - <i>mote'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H4131\">H4131</a>; a <i>wavering</i>, that is, <i>fall</i>; by implication a <i>pole</i> (as shaking); hence a <i>yoke</i> (as essentially a bent pole): - bar, be moved, staff, yoke."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4131\">H4131</a>, <a href=\"#/H4133\">H4133</a>"}]}